Title: Mapping .NET Timestamps to PostgreSQL
Description: Npgsql 6.0 contains some significant changes to how timestamps are mapped between .NET and PostgreSQL - most applications will need to react to this (although a compatibility flag exists). This post gives the context for these changes, going over the timestamp types on both sides and the problems in mapping them.
